A Research Associate position is currently available in Nanyang Environment &amp; Water Research Institute - Advanced Environmental Biotechnology Centre (NEWRI-AEBC).

Job Responsibilities

  Support research work on wastewater-based epidemiology by performing advanced statistical data analysis of the measurements
  Prepare data for presentations
  Prepare reports on the work

Job Requirements:

  Master’s degree in Civil and Environmental Engineering
  Knowledge and experience on statistical data analysis (e.g. Descriptive Statistics, Bivariate Analysis, Regression Analyses, and Fit Logistic Regression, or some of these)
  Knowledge of probability theory and statistical inference
  A minimum 1-year research experience on uncertainty estimation
  Highly motivated person who is able to work independently
  Good communication skills &amp; team player

We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.